<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM1.7">
<l>uraikkap paṭuvatu moṉṟuṇṭu kēṭkiṟcev vāṉtoṭaimē</l>
<l>liraikkiṉṟa pāmpiṉai yeṉṟun toṭēliḻin tōṭṭanteṅkun</l>
<l>tiraikkiṉṟa kaṅkaiyun tēṉṉiṉṟa koṉṟaiyuñ ceñcaṭaimēl</l>
<l>viraikkiṉṟa vaṉṉiyuñ ceṉṉit talaivaitta vētiyaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you listen to one thing that is said [to you], don’t ever touch the snake</l>
<l>that hisses on the wreath(?) in the red sky – o Veda master who puts on [his] head</l>
<l>on top the Gaṅgā that, wherever it descends [and] runs, rises,</l>
<l>the Laburnun on which honey stays and the fragrant fire on the red matted locks.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
